snippet.textDisplay:
we are not lactose intolerant - we're just not baby cows ;) Your skin and hair looks better because your body got rid of all toxins from animal products. And you feel better and more positive because you don't consume dead flesh - Think of it as a karma. I really wish you can stay vegan and hopefully it will be easier for you in the future. Most fast food places are adapting to growing "trend" and now offer vegan options (like beyond burgers and what not) so hopefully you will have more options when going out with friends and maybe even inspire them to try vegan. It's so much better for you, for the animals, and for the environment.
Other great movies to watch (other than Cowspiracy which you have seen) is Earthlings (narrated by Jouquin Phoenix), What the Health and Game Changers.
Wish you all the best ad so happy you discovered and try veganism!
xo
